How I burn movies:

 modprobe ide-cd
 hendry@scrooge-15:~/movie$ mkhybrid -o /tmp/foo.iso -r -J Dirty_Dancing_DVDrip_XVID_westerrecords.avi 
 cdrecord -scanbus dev=ATAPI:
 cdrecord -prcap
 cdrecord -v speed=24 driveropts=burnfree dev=ATAPI:0,0 /tmp/foo.iso
